----------------------------------------------------------------------

  Field                A:Db1    A:Db2    A:Db3  |     C:Db1    C:Db2    C:Db3
  ----------------  -------- -------- --------  |  -------- -------- --------
  Q_L(3,2,1/6)          1/15        1      2/3  |      1/15        1      1/3
  u_R(3,1,2/3)          8/15        0      1/3  |      8/15        0      1/6
  d_R(3,1,-1/3)         2/15        0      1/3  |      2/15        0      1/6
  L_L(1,2,-1/2)          1/5      1/3        0  |       1/5      1/3        0
  e_R(1,1,-1)            2/5        0        0  |       2/5        0        0
  ----------------  -------- -------- --------  |  -------- -------- --------
  Per generation         4/3      4/3      4/3  |       4/3      4/3      2/3

  Three generations (A): 4, 4, 4
  Three generations (C): 4, 4, 2

